/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要買野就一係黃店，一係網購外國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c4a78be048ac1a2577ea0d31cbf947ad6c9b5d","tid":1690703,"uid":55658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc5e06c9b336ec3db7e1694d5a008af77cc3a2e0","tid":1690703,"uid":115689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"勇武亦唔會停<br />\n小隊形式快閃<br />\n<br />\n和理非街坊裝分散狗力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"最好平日搞"},{"pid":"be5c9e6d2ee8f4616a1c34079b36964d4007641c","tid":1690703,"uid":293912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"仲有，除咗霸鐵，仲要唔喺黨鐵站同黨鐵旗下商場嘅商店作任何消費"},{"pid":"9275ad1d8407cae5700ee1806a3fd0f39d4c5a58","tid":1690703,"uid":115689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b48603f5299326cb596157b66d1deba622eb6a","tid":1690703,"uid":293912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"Support<br />\n<br />\n不過爆支持黃店可唔可以唔係一日，而係幾多日都得？有啲人已經係自己日日做，但如果只係 promote 一星期一日，有啲人就會真係只做一日，一星期幫襯藍店六日。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"其實我日日都係<br />\n不過爆買嘅意思係要黃藍兩方都睇得到<br />\n食就七日都藍店<br />\n買嘢可以推響星期四<br />\n<br />\n8!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b7c87b786c6e6bf0de6e0f4f3071aeb83a8888","tid":1690703,"uid":241501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"18b8be5a56c4e5635b432d2011b8372f1621e5cf","tid":1690703,"uid":115689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c4a78be048ac1a2577ea0d31cbf947ad6c9b5d","tid":1690703,"uid":55658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc5e06c9b336ec3db7e1694d5a008af77cc3a2e0","tid":1690703,"uid":115689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"勇武亦唔會停<br />\n小隊形式快閃<br />\n<br />\n和理非街坊裝分散狗力"},"citedB